---
title: Spiced Chicken & Peri-Peri Bacon Jam with Crushed Potatoes & Avocado Salad
description: We’re pulling out the big guns tonight and blasting away your tastebuds with a saucy bacon jam. The ammunition to bring this spiced chicken dinner to victory is the peri peri sauce.
